Re: Practising via manga
by Akiahara » Fri 06.20.2008 4:18 pm Well, this isn't really for studying or anything, but since it is manga-ish and in Japanese, I thought I'd post it.This image is sorta big.これは市丸ギンです。ブリーチ漫画から。Ichimaru Gin... from the Bleach manga. He says... "ikorose"... "shinsou". I'm not familiar with these kanji, but they're from the manga, so I don't know if the usage is irregular. I believe the translation is "shoot to death/to kill, divine spear."
